public class Element30
extends Element3D

Class for Element30. Properties of element are; Mechanics: Solid, Geometric: Linear, Material: Orthotropic/Isotropic, Interpolation degree: Trilinear, Interpolation family: Lagrange, Number of nodes: 4, Geometry: Tetrahedral, Dofs (per node): ux, uy, uz (global), u1, u2, u3 (local), Mechanical loading: fx, fy, fz (global), f1, f2, f3 (local), Temperature loading: yes, Displacements: u1, u2, u3, Strains: e11, e22, e33, e12, e13, e23 Stresses: s11, s22, s33, s12, s13, s23.

Author:
Murat
